//program-think.blogspot.com/2012/12/system-vm-4.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2704948640969790443","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/2704948640969790443","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2013年12月14日 00:18:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"D08ER34zfip7ImA9XBBRFE8.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-6040789074932250164"},"published":{"$t":"2019-07-06T23:10:06.086+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2019-07-06T23:10:06.086+08:00"},"app$edited":{"xmlns$app":"http://www.w3.org/2007/app","$t":"2019-07-06T23:10:06.086+08:00"},"title":{"$t":"TO 加国小留\n针对你的几个问题，俺逐一回复如下：\n\n========\n\n1、\n俺比较赞同 1单元 ..."},"content":{"type":"html","$t":"TO 加国小留<br />针对你的几个问题，俺逐一回复如下：<br /><br />========<br /><br />1、<br />俺比较赞同 1单元 提到的观点。<br />1.1<br />这几个国家，除了越南与天朝的文化比较接近，其它几个的文化差距太大，而且意识形态也不同。<br />这些国家与中国达成某种“经济同盟”的可能性很小。<br />目前川普的套路是——<br />他反对 WTO 这种一揽子的做法；他倾向于跟每个国家单独谈贸易协议。<br />1.2<br />越南与印度，都在天朝周边，而且都有领土纠纷。<br />这两个国家都想要借助美国来制衡中国。<br />（注：早些年，印度是借助“苏/俄”来制衡中国；如今开始向美国靠拢）<br /><br />2、<br />你这个表述不太对。<br />你想说的大概是——美国国务院的某个官员重提【文明冲突论】。<br />正好俺在这篇博文中也提到了——亨廷顿的这个代表作。<br /><br />3、<br />俺觉得与“贸易战”是否出现，关系不大。<br />不管有没有贸易战，“脑残”依然是“脑残”；<br />而已经摆脱洗脑的人，也不会因为贸易战而重新变成脑残。<br /><br />4、<br />俺写过一些【反洗脑】的博文，你可以参考一下：<br />《[url=https://program-think.blogspot.com/2014/02/brainwash-and-idiot.html]聊聊洗脑和脑残——分析“脑残的起源”和“脑残的觉醒”[/url]》<br />《[url=https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/03/Why-Thinking-Hard-So-Hard.html]为什么独立思考这么难？——谈谈心理学的成因，并分享俺的经验[/url]》<br />《[url=https://program-think.blogspot.com/2014/05/fans-and-idolatry.html]不要成为“粉丝”——谈谈“偶像崇拜”的成因和危害[/url]》<br />《[url=https://program-think.blogspot.com/2012/12/emperor-complex.html]天朝民众的心理分析：圣君情结[/url]》<br />《[url=https://program-think.blogspot.com/2012/06/stockholm-syndrome.html]天朝民众的心理分析：斯德哥尔摩综合症[/url]》<br />《[url=https://program-think.blogspot.com/2014/01/doublethink.html]比“欺骗”更有效的洗脑手法——基于【双重思想】的思维控制[/url]》<br />《[url=https://program-think.blogspot.com/2014/12/brainwash-using-real-data.html]比“欺骗”更狡猾的洗脑——基于【真实数据】进行忽悠[/url]》"},"link":[{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2877954000317338528/comments/default/6040789074932250164?v=2"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2877954000317338528/comments/default/6040789074932250164?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/07/Misunderstand-China-USA-Relations.html?showComment=1562425806086#c6040789074932250164","title":"澄清&#8220;中美对抗&#8221;常见的一些&#12304;误解&#12305;"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2877954000317338528/comments/default/5150761999090688957?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg?cache=36c4cca294ae50025f1c139a5907df5d"}}],"thr$in-reply-to":{"xmlns$thr":"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/07/Misunderstand-China-USA-Relations.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2877954000317338528","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/2877954000317338528","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2019年7月6日 23:10:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"DEEMQnk-fCp7ImA9WhBQE08.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-1691924570570085211"},"published":{"$t":"2013-03-15T13:51:23.754+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2013-03-15T13:51:23.754+08:00"},"app$edited"